        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And then… nothing happens. The system doesn’t notify anyone.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Now you’ve got frustrated customers asking why there wasn’t a follow-up, or an angry client wondering why their chatbot isn’t doing what you promised.",
